result.name: Wing Chun Vietnam Restaurant - Lion Rock Road

reviews.text: I was ordered the traditional raw beef with rice noodles (pho) with a hot drink set in the late afternoon.  The soup was exceptionally fatty and full of MSG.  The beef was rough. Price was very decent for an afternoon set but I was very thirsty afterwards even I had tried to filter the oil and just drank a few spoonfuls of the soup.  The bowl and the chopsticks were of strong smell of bleach.
Reasonable price, average food
Good quality, tasty food , alought the decoration is not very good , but it is still a very good one . The price of food is not high either .

Delicious Thai and Vietnamese food in a typical Hong Kong restaurant- cursory but fast service.  Highly recommend the satay noodles or rice, which were loved.  Other dishes were good also, such as the pho, everyone liked their food.
Food abd service are good.

result.name: 永珍越南食館 - 獅子石道

reviews.text: 永珍有越南同泰國餐館，兩間鋪都係響隔離，餐牌有齊越南同泰國菜。食物味道不錯，火車頭越南粉超大碗，好足料，女仔肯定食唔晒！越式滴漏咖啡既煉奶另上都係第一次見。員工友善，服務態度好好。

I was ordered the traditional raw beef with rice noodles (pho) with a hot drink set in the late afternoon.  The soup was exceptionally fatty and full of MSG.  The beef was rough. Price was very decent for an afternoon set but I was very thirsty afterwards even I had tried to filter the oil and just drank a few spoonfuls of the soup.  The bowl and the chopsticks were of strong smell of bleach.
九龍城其中ㄧ間較出色的泰式及越式餐廳。更重要是她是素食有善餐廳,樂意為素食者提供有關服務。
Reasonable price, average food

用料不錯
我點了火車頭河粉
份量足夠
很多牛腩和牛根

不過要扣分的地方
在飲品方面
我叫了茶走
但是完全沒有煉奶
味道澀到苦的
因此扣咗一粒星
😅😅😅
